nodes.text: Theed Palace Space Vessel Engineering Corps

The Theed Palace Space Vessel Engineering Corps, also known as Theed Palace Engineering Corps, was a manufacturing company that designed and built starships for the human denizens of Naboo. Their products included the N-1 starfighter, the Naboo Royal Starship (based on a J-type 327 Nubian starship), and the J-type diplomatic barge.
